-- Would You Pay $1M for This Electric Supercar?
-- B y
-- 2012-05-18T01:05:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-18/would-you-pay-1m-for-this-electric-supercar-.html
Croatian carmaker Rimac Auto has 
announced it will put into production the Concept One electric 
supercar, a concept vehicle that first made waves at last 
year's Frankfurt Auto Show. The battery-powered vehicle boasts 
more than 1,000 Hp and reaches a top speed of 190 Mph. Only 88 
are expected to be sold worldwide in 2013. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 00:37
 